def test_demo(self):
        try:
            # 初始化发现页操作类（传入self即可复用所有minium对象）
            hom_page = HomePage(self)

            # 链式调用公共方法，逻辑清晰
            hom_page.goto_home_page()

            # 点击左上角 个人中心 头像
            user_btn = self.page.get_element(home_user_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            user_btn.click()

            user_btn_list = self.page.get_elements(home_user_btn_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            for user_btn in user_btn_list:
                # 查找日程管理的btn
                if user_btn.text == home_user_schedule_btn_name:
                    user_btn.click()

            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"日程管理后_{timestamp}", region=self.page)
            time.sleep(1)

            create_btn = self.page.get_element(home_user_schedule_create_btn_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            create_btn.click()
            print(f"点击创建btn成功")

        except Exception as e:
            self.logger.error(f"日程管理失败：{str(e)}")
            # 异常时截图
            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"日程管理失败_{timestamp}")

            time.sleep(1)

            raise

        time.sleep(2)
